{"tid":541330,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"台中去花蓮交通！","createTime":"2018-01-26T10:00:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-28T14:09:07.000Z","uid":25773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"32154e6f9afd7633ce374dd312b8300a3609d398","tid":541330,"uid":25773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T10:00:26.000Z","msg":"小弟二月會去台中加花蓮7日6夜，喺ZUJI買左套票搭hkexpress去台中<br />\n(但第4日先喺台中住，第1日會即刻搭車去花蓮) <br />\n我上網見人話冇車直到花蓮，要搭左高鐵去台北轉車會方便啲<br />\n<br />\n但我第4日都會喺花蓮返台中，到時又會再搭返去台北再去台中，每程買單程飛加埋都要16，1700台幣左右<br />\n<br />\n到底點買先係最平？好似話有來回既車飛買到？有冇巴絲打幫手解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5964709536b26e211cce8213ed8e4706e9a0ef3","tid":541330,"uid":25773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T10:00:44.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"918696a5a83f86aa95eab83ef3fa7a1e102a1cb5","tid":541330,"uid":25773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T10:03:06.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f095731b2cf53adbd31b8937870c0a89fce157b","tid":541330,"uid":25773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T10:12:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/face